---
title: Beef & Bacon Fettuccine Bolognese with Fresh Pasta, Asparagus Salad & Pesto Panini
description: Packed with the rich flavours of a classic Italian tomato sauce, you'll find it hard to believe this beef and bacon bolognese didn't involve hours of cooking. Enjoy it alongside a pesto-packed hasselback panini, adding even more flavour to this already delicious meal.
